<p>
  <code>whatcable --monitor</code> streams live power and cable state to your terminal as plain text. <code>whatcable --monitor-json</code> outputs the same data as newline-delimited JSON for scripting and log pipelines.
</p>

<h3>Widget power sparkline <span class="pro-badge">Pro</span></h3>
<p>
  The desktop widget shows a live power chart alongside cable status. Glance at your desktop and see charging trends without opening anything.
</p>

